    "ParMETIS",
    "netCDF",
    "HDF5",

    "matrix.base"
  ],
  "resources": [
    "PBS",
    "Cray Development Tools",
    "Cray netCDF",
    "Cray HDF5",
    "PrgEnv-cray",
    "PrgEnv-gnu",
    "PrgEnv-intel"
  ],
  "notes": [
    "This script runs a matrix of regression tests for WAVEWATCH III on a Cray XC architecture.",
    "It uses a variety of compilers, libraries, and tools, including Cray CCE, GNU Fortran, Intel Fortran, ParMETIS, netCDF, HDF5, and SNP Launcher.",

    "The script also uses a variety of environment variables to control the execution of the tests."
  ]
}
